07182530.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/180201iFCEE28DE324F92B1/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="sebastian_wilhelm1_3-1729107182530.png" alt="sebastian_wilhelm1_3-1729107182530.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="sebastian_wilhelm1_4-1729107263238.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/180202i83DDD13E2CB34921/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="sebastian_wilhelm1_4-1729107263238.png" alt="sebastian_wilhelm1_4-1729107263238.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Does anyone know how to solve this issue or is there any other approach?&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Thanks and regards, Sebastian&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;</content>
